Review.Titre: A perfect way to avoid time waste, frustration and understand how to climb
Review.Contenu: Were do I start. So the guys here are doing a relentless job at doing their best even in desperate situations. They did complete my effective request and they did it in a good final rush. Honda is always online for any concern and, after speaking to him, I'm sure they are trying to fill an immense load of requests. What went wrong: I can't go down to 3 starts because, in the end, I appreciate the work of this guys and I don't wanna be the nit picker of the situation, though must be said that the communication with my booster were practically absent and I got only random answers. To this day there are still a lot of things I don't know which would have been resolved with a quick confrontation. Indeed, I feel like more than one guy did climb using my profile and maybe it would be good to know that and to have some minor chit-chat with the new acquaintance. In the end you know that you will get what've paid for but, for me at least, not necessarily more than that. Which is quite good obviously, but could be improved just a little tiny bit of communication. In the end I will leave 4 star as you can see and wish all the best to the guys.

Hopefully they learn for next time so they can service us low-elo players better.

Review.Contenu: I have ordered 3 wins in diamond 3, in general, it took quite a while to complete my boosting due to booster's on-going life and social issue, and it was quite a long wait for me as a customer. Important thing here is that not all the boosters will smash your ranks with 100% win rate, but they will also lose sometimes when they meet bad teammates, or they have on-going life issues. The latter case, it will let you to wait a little bit more time than your expectation. In this perspective, the most important part of this servicing is communication between customers and the service providers. The whole communication with Lol-eloboosting team was efficient and satisfying enough to wait for the delay and their communication skills to alternate and control the situation was fairly appropriate. Shortly, Lol-eloboosting service will do their best to satisfy their customers even though we, as customers, encounter unexpected situations. Finally, I will recommend this service if you want to have a good experience. Thanks.
